snippet.title: Roma and Diana vs Pesky Flies! Аnd other Funny Stories by Kids Diana Show
snippet.description:
Roma and Diana were playing. But suddenly flies appeared and disturbed them. Roma and Diana came up with how to get rid of pesky flies. 
Diana Builds Playhouse for the Minion. Kids pretend play and create funny stories for children's videos.
